53e82b9a8cb7b57867fd77a8b4f4a0d7d9e9246479f1bb7b23b9586c68d1712271316e8c17545e9fd1daee3ecd1ac587b2c7dcdb42518d00537c580594c53059  fix-makefile.patch
"
